{"tid":1008252,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實真係好憎食團年飯","createTime":"2019-02-04T10:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T11:37:54.000Z","uid":84396,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"16cd98443efb898c23c25d79e5da5ddcfcb390ac","tid":1008252,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:50:34.000Z","msg":"家族人比較多 每年團年都好多人會黎我屋企<br />\n啲親戚有幾煩 咁多位巴絲都應該見識過<br />\n年年過年屋企就好似城市論壇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班廢老睇新聞 就逐個以為好有見地咁討論<br />\n睇完新聞到食飯 就逐個後輩問長問短<br />\n然後又逐個由頭數到落腳指尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係寧願扮要返工 唔返黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：收左工扮未收 係街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dab013c50776b37f15fd5528c8444fcc5a1acf6","tid":1008252,"uid":73463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:51:17.000Z","msg":"問長問短好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89625b73ebb53165d992342bc4aacf7c54906e8","tid":1008252,"uid":84396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0dab013c50776b37f15fd5528c8444fcc5a1acf6","tid":1008252,"uid":73463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:51:17.000Z","msg":"問長問短好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:57:14.000Z","msg":"問你唔係為左關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係為左踩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1724a3749cf2e